Holiday Party & New Year's Celebration Half Case_
                    Six bottles for a sensational holiday party                

                        If you're hosting a holiday party, save yourself a trip to the wine shop. This six-pack has everything you need: two sparkling wines, one white and three robust reds. In fact, if you order this half case ... mind inviting us over, too? Kidding aside, wine is the last thing you should have to worry about for your holiday festivities. Spend your time and effort on the food and the invite list.  read more...
                    

